Nigerian superstar, Davido has spoken on being responsible for alleged pregnancy of an anonymous lady making the rounds on social media. A viral video on Tuesday emerged showing two girls accusing Davido of being responsible for a pregnancy. One of the girls said Davido allegedly slept with her at Eko hotel and got her pregnant. However, Davido in a swift reaction threatened to take the girls to court even as he denied being responsible for the pregnancy. On his Twitter page, he wrote: “Your pregnancy na audio money, these hoes going to jail mark my words. “You all taking this clout chasing and social media shit too far!! “I will go to the end of the world and use all my power to make sure them hoes end up in prison.” This is coming few days after his fiancée, Chioma delivered a baby boy for him. VIDEO:   A post shared by nwachukwu john owen (@realjohn_owen) on Oct 23, 2019 at 5:25am PDT  Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.